description: With this skill, you can easily find out what is for breakfast or lunch at any school in Henrico County, Virginia.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Henrico County Schools what is for lunch today at Pemberton?
Alexa ask Henrico County Schools what is for breakfast on Friday at Freeman High School?

name: Henrico County Schools
shortDescription: Complete breakfast and lunch menus for Henrico County Public Schools.
